Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那两人是在何种状况下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}进行着何种对话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至连我自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不曾了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 这个是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但仅仅是看着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就感到无比难受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月…学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对于面对自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很是畏惧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 害羞鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说…我为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑到这儿应该就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 那女生也太强硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了 请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说…说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不快点 会被柠檬学姐骂的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要回房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总算回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们俩 究竟去干嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人老师教了我一些演技的诀窍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老师可是完美主义者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是些小事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起这个…学姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有啥事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说比起这个…一夏学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}听…听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可是罪犯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}树下她…突然就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}无论怎样…都不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}要是钱我多少还是有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐突然就出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一无所知的我 胶片还在运转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}这…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}啊 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…有些尴尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}在哪在哪 在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}那里那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}哪里！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了 放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是为什么 来到这个星球的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有…还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有真正的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你喜欢小海吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才这个景 换个角度再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川 麻烦你拿一下包包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱 换地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吓到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐也来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我现在正与电影之神进行电波交流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 千春？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真刺激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(642,664)}aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是叫有泽…来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那女生挺可爱的 哲朗和她交往算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这种话…可不能对哲朗说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同学 你能代替他拿下反光板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍摄 要继续了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要拍得可爱点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗一去不复返
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱千载空悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐也不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…海人 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学他 刚才悄悄走出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去树下同学那里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他…果然对树下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么能这么断定？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看就…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…不介意的话能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…心意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 让我们好好谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.37,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}活力饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:08:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}703号室的树下小姐现在外出不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请问是叫雾岛先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有树下小姐给您的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请等等~哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说都跑了几小时了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她是铁人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请等等我~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 这么害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又被你救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢啊 美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}帮我保密的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是温柔呢 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还行吧 不过只限于对可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好过分啊 哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}东躲西藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然我也不讨厌这样的Play就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 我们继续享受约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至…至今为止的那算是约会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把人家叫出来还迟到 然后沉默不语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 我还没整理好自己的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…我有事想好好问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…树下同学对海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…是怎么看的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果我这么说的话 你会怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在戏弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 因为有点羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得哲朗感到很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么会觉得困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对吧 哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 你喜欢哲朗先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这种…明明就是个暴露狂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你跑进来的时候没有穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这很奇怪吧 很奇怪不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不穿内裤到处走 想像着被别人看到而感到兴奋的变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被这种女孩子喜欢哲朗也不愿意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裸族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是…裸族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被 被甩了是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被海人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是啦 是被在东京的学校里的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来冲绳是为了心碎旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.47,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}日文写作伤心旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后就碰巧再会小海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起闹闹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想借此掩盖掉被男朋友甩掉后寂寞的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为这样…给你们添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么你那时候会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和被男朋友甩掉时所说的完全相同的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从小海口中说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回想起了往事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不经意间就哭了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时 小海这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他说“我有喜欢的人了”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想 那一定是在说你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在说什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看小海那样我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再怎么说 我和他姑且也是青梅竹马哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你心里也是一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 这算赔罪咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}树下同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天的拍摄也请多关照罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}赔罪是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是被树下叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 为什么学姐会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一定 已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 差不多该告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 如果你能穿上这件衣服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.19,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}导演你是不是错过了很重要的一段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？还要穿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裸族？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…裸族是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那种…在家里都是过着全裸自在生活的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 家人也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我从小也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我以为在家里都这样所以就是理所当然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上小学后就开始觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是这种事又不能对谁说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道穿内衣是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我有很严重的低血压
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶尔会忘了穿内衣就这么去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道这样下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}尝试矫正了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是偶尔还是会犯这毛病…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我想那就不要引人注目就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就让自己变得透明起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是面对这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜还是来和我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗和雾岛同学也愿意做我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我实在…太高兴了…太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才不想被你们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是变态…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}经常忘记的话把替换衣物预先放进包里不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后装作去上厕所把它穿上就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}体操服什么的还是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}慌个手忙脚乱也解决不了问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么叫变得透明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太过消极思考了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有烦恼就找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜也是 海也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被大家讨厌了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你信不过我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以呢 有什么想说的就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}树下她 有过这样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她说“对不起”了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊 我真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明已经察觉到她在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}却没有好好听她诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结果变成“交给学姐”这种形式解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想树下同学她其实是想对海人你诉说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先一步把她叫了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把树下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 所以白天的时候你才会在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有什么话要对她说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总觉得啊 那两个人间的气氛很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反而我倒成了电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生明明说过没有喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我这样到底是多像个小丑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明只是来陪我的碎心旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结果大家都一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}货真价实的天然…太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}害我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真伤脑筋呐 这个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天色晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他们在担心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才的答复 不用说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同学他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说不定现在还被和树下一起的那个女孩纠缠着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然 被女孩子那样猛追的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作为男生不会动什么歪脑筋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 多少有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}树下同学那时候也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别欺负我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我并不想被追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而是想去追别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去追我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…如果我的心意让学姐感到困扰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我没有…感到困扰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们在做什么喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.55,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}救护车！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷谷谷 谷川同学！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊 我们什么都没做话说你那是什么打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们两个孤男寡女的去了哪里喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 你们到底跑哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 这怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只不过我们两个女孩子开了个小会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐 我亲~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什么呢 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那海人也来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗喵和美樱喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们俩跑去哪了喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 你们都跑哪里去了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}过分过分！只留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好困…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能在这里睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这到底什么情况！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你竟然为了保护我而…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样一来树下的戏份就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摄影结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么我因为要赶飞机 就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思啊 让你拖到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍摄要加油啊 完成之后一定要让我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}树下同学 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再这么呆头呆脑的 我就把小海抢走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 有一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟是初恋情人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们是傍晚的班机来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是下午五点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的摄影到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}东西收好以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就好好享受冲绳的大海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…对海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬说要大家一起去逛庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那真是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}散发着阴谋的气息啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
